cs_alley [Inspired by cs_backalley]
by: P.M.Hampton [Pakkun]
textures by various artists

***NOTICE***
The map takes place early in the morning hours to 
incorperate night vision. A few areas are pitch 
black and require a flashlight. There is an 
alternate hostage rescue point in this map! It's
located on the right from the CT spawn or the 
left of the T spawn.
